name: My Precious ꜩ
description:
The term “Tezos” (ꜩ) is ancient Greek for “smart contract”, according to the developers. 

Trying to meet new things, break out of old habits, learn a language I've never known before, and be in a truly magical world. Maybe that's why Tezos as a symbol is quite interesting for me. Because this symbol for me is the key that opens the gate for me to a new world.
